审计app.py代码

flask框架

```python
from flask import Flask, request, send_file, render_template_string
import os
from urllib.parse import urlparse, urlunparse
import subprocess
import socket
import hashlib
import base64
import random

app = Flask(__name__)
BlackList = [
    "127.0.0.1"
]

if __name__ == '__main__':
    app.run(host='0.0.0.0', port=8000)
```

